<i>adjective</i>: 괄괄하다 [괄괄하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>괄괄하다 [괄괄하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hot-tempered; ardent</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 몹시 강하고 급하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a very strong and impetuous personality.</dd><br>
<dd>2. robust</dd><br>
<dd>목소리가 굵고 거칠면서 크다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a deep, tough and loud voice.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>